    q: "How often can you use a sauna blanket?",
    a: "Most healthy adults can use one several times a week, and daily is fine once you tolerate the heat well - start with two or three shorter sessions a week and build up. Listen to your body, keep early sessions to 30 minutes or so, hydrate before and after, and skip a session if you feel unwell, lightheaded, or dehydrated.",
